{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"position","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"added"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This function should only be called by classes implementing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListModel","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". It has to be called after the internal representation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"list"},{"type":"text","text":" has been updated, because handlers connected to this signal"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"might query the new state of the list.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Implementations must only make changes to the model (as visible to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its consumer) in places that will not cause problems for that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"consumer.  For models that are driven directly by a write API (such"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"), changes can be reported in response to uses of that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"API.  For models that represent remote data, changes should only be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"made from a fresh mainloop dispatch.  It is particularly not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"permitted to make changes in response to a call to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListModel","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumer API.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Stated another way: in general, it is assumed that code making a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"series of accesses to the model via the API, without returning to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"mainloop, and without calling other code, will continue to view the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"same contents of the model.","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListModelRef\/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"position"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"removed"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"added"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"title":"itemsChanged(position:removed:add